description: This common Plezier purrs with a rating of 39, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 39, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 1 for East, Stringalong for South, and Stringalong for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [39 Votes, Common]
